{"an5.217:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 5.217 ","an5.217:0.2":"22. Akkosakavagga ","an5.217:0.3":"Pathamaapasadikasutta ","an5.217:1.1":"“Pancime, bhikkhave, adinava apasadike. ","an5.217:1.2":"Katame panca? ","an5.217:1.3":"Attapi attanam upavadati, ","an5.217:1.4":"anuvicca vinnu garahanti, ","an5.217:1.5":"papako kittisaddo abbhuggacchati, ","an5.217:1.6":"sammulho kalam karoti, ","an5.217:1.7":"kayassa bheda param marana apayam duggatim vinipatam nirayam upapajjati. ","an5.217:1.8":"Ime kho, bhikkhave, panca adinava apasadike. ","an5.217:2.1":"Pancime, bhikkhave, anisamsa pasadike. ","an5.217:2.2":"Katame panca? ","an5.217:2.3":"Attapi attanam na upavadati, ","an5.217:2.4":"anuvicca vinnu pasamsanti, ","an5.217:2.5":"kalyano kittisaddo abbhuggacchati, ","an5.217:2.6":"asammulho kalam karoti, ","an5.217:2.7":"kayassa bheda param marana sugatim saggam lokam upapajjati. ","an5.217:2.8":"Ime kho, bhikkhave, panca anisamsa pasadike”ti. ","an5.217:2.9":"Sattamam. "}